Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.95,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:15.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:15.37,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:20.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:20.96,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.59,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}而我卻要目送你離開
