Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.05,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.13,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.72,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我們終將會重來
